==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Ure
<hw>Ure</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To use; to exercise; to inure; to
accustom by practice.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The French soldiers . . . from their youth have been practiced and
<qex>ured</qex> in feats of arms.</q> <rj><qau>Sir T.
More.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

